#: ../../source/getting_started/installation.rst:2
msgid "Access and installation"
msgstr "访问与安装"

#: ../../source/getting_started/installation.rst:5
msgid "Enable MaxFrame for your MaxCompute project"
msgstr "为您的MaxCompute项目启用MaxFrame"

#: ../../source/getting_started/installation.rst:6
msgid ""
"You need to setup a MaxCompute project Before using MaxFrame. Please take"
" a look at `here <https://www.alibabacloud.com/zh/product/maxcompute>`_ "
"for more information."
msgstr ""
"在使用MaxFrame之前，您需要设置一个MaxCompute项目。请查看`此处 <https://"
"www.alibabacloud.com/zh/product/maxcompute>`_获取更多信息。"

#: ../../source/getting_started/installation.rst:11
msgid ""
"Currently MaxFrame is under trial. If you need to enable MaxFrame for "
"your MaxCompute project, please `fill the form to apply for trial "
"<https://survey.aliyun.com/apps/zhiliao/m40AIrxhA?spm=a2c4g.11186623.0.0.a69340f2mJENKJ>`_"
" here."
msgstr ""
"目前MaxFrame正处于试用阶段。如果您需要为您的MaxCompute项目启用MaxFrame，"
"请`填写表单申请试用 <https://survey.aliyun.com/apps/zhiliao/m40AIrxhA?spm"
"=a2c4g.11186623.0.0.a69340f2mJENKJ>`_。"

#: ../../source/getting_started/installation.rst:16
msgid "Install MaxFrame client locally"
msgstr "在本地安装MaxFrame客户端"

#: ../../source/getting_started/installation.rst:17
msgid ""
"After created your own MaxCompute project and enabled MaxFrame, you may "
"install MaxFrame client with `pip` command:"
msgstr ""
"在创建了您自己的MaxCompute项目并启用了MaxFrame之后，您可以使用`pip`命令"
"安装MaxFrame客户端："

#: ../../source/getting_started/installation.rst:24
msgid ""
"Then you can create a MaxCompute table, perform some transformation with "
"MaxFrame and then store the result into another MaxCompute table."
msgstr ""
"然后您可以创建一个MaxCompute表，使用MaxFrame进行一些转换操作，然后将结果"
"存储到另一个MaxCompute表中。"

#: ../../source/getting_started/installation.rst:59
msgid "Access MaxFrame with DataWorks"
msgstr "通过DataWorks访问MaxFrame"

#: ../../source/getting_started/installation.rst:60
msgid ""
"DataWorks provides task scheduling capability for MaxCompute projects. "
"You can schedule and run MaxFrame job with DataWorks."
msgstr ""
"DataWorks为MaxCompute项目提供了任务调度能力。您可以通过DataWorks调度和"
"运行MaxFrame作业。"

#: ../../source/getting_started/installation.rst:63
msgid ""
"To run MaxFrame job with DataWorks, you need to create a PyODPS 3 node "
"and write your code inside it. PyODPS nodes are executed with embedded "
"MaxCompute accounts and project information, thus you may create your "
"MaxFrame session directly."
msgstr ""
"要通过DataWorks运行MaxFrame作业，您需要创建一个PyODPS 3节点并在其中编写"
"代码。PyODPS节点会嵌入MaxCompute账户和项目信息执行，因此您可以直接创建"
"MaxFrame会话。"

#: ../../source/getting_started/installation.rst:84
msgid "Access MaxFrame with MaxCompute Notebook"
msgstr "通过MaxCompute Notebook访问MaxFrame"

#: ../../source/getting_started/installation.rst:85
msgid ""
"`MaxCompute Notebook <https://help.aliyun.com/zh/maxcompute/user-guide"
"/maxcompute-notebook-instruction>`_ also provides MaxFrame package. It "
"also provides MaxCompute account in environment variables in the "
"notebook, thus account information is not needed."
msgstr ""
"`MaxCompute Notebook <https://help.aliyun.com/zh/maxcompute/user-guide/"
"maxcompute-notebook-instruction>`_也提供了MaxFrame包。它还在notebook的"
"环境变量中提供了MaxCompute账户信息，因此不需要额外提供账户信息。"

